## Additional Acknowledgments

This project was built with assistance from Kiro AI, demonstrating the power of 
AI-assisted software development for rapid prototyping and comprehensive testing.

### Third-Party Libraries and Services

This project uses the following third-party services and libraries:

- AWS Bedrock (Amazon Web Services) - AI language models
- React.js (Meta) - Frontend framework
- Node.js - JavaScript runtime
- Express.js - Web application framework
- Material-UI - React component library
- Redis - In-memory data structure store
- Docker - Containerization platform

### Data Sources

Sample agricultural price data is based on publicly available market information
and is used for demonstration purposes only. Actual market prices may vary.

